---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout title="小學部課程介紹 | 光禾華德福">
  <Navigation />
  
  <section class="hero-small">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>小學部課程介紹</h1>
      <p>主課程與副課程</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>主課程</h2>
        <p>華德福的主課程是一個週期性狀態，透過這個歷程讓學生專注且持續約三至四週的學習，課程領域包含：文史、自然、數學等。在學習歷程中學生透過課程藝術化的引導吸收所學的「知識」，並透過充分的睡眠，經由隔天在課堂上的「回顧與重述」，讓經驗轉化成自己的能力，並書寫在自己的工作本上。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>109-111學年度課程圖像</h2>
        
        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>一年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>穹蒼班</strong> - 自然日 聆聽大地的聲音</li>
            <li><strong>銀杏班</strong> - 語文課</li>
            <li><strong>澄月班</strong> - 學習樣貌</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>二年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>海洋班</strong> - 數學課</li>
            <li><strong>暖陽班</strong> - 語文課</li>
            <li><strong>銀杏班</strong> - 語文課</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>三年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>雲彩班</strong> - 農耕課 種自己的米</li>
            <li><strong>海洋班</strong> - 建築課</li>
            <li><strong>暖陽班</strong> - 建築課</li>
            <li><strong>農耕課</strong></li>
            <li><strong>語文課</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>四年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>茉莉班</strong> - 人與動物王國</li>
            <li><strong>雲彩班</strong> - 地方探究 探尋左營舊城</li>
            <li><strong>海洋班</strong> - 分數</li>
            <li><strong>人與動物與農場</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>五年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>芙蓉班</strong> - 山林活動</li>
            <li><strong>茉莉班</strong> - 數學幾何</li>
            <li><strong>雲彩班</strong> - 燈影下的傳承</li>
            <li><strong>古文明 希臘</strong></li>
            <li><strong>植物課</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>六年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>榕樹班</strong> - 商業數學</li>
            <li><strong>茉莉班</strong> - 跨越之旅</li>
            <li><strong>芙蓉班</strong> - 羅馬</li>
            <li><strong>聲光熱</strong></li>
            <li><strong>尺規幾何</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>107-108學年度課程圖像</h2>
        
        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>一年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>數學 - 加減乘除精靈</li>
            <li>自然日</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>二年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>注音課</li>
            <li>數學 - 魔法圓盤</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>三年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>建築課與露營</li>
            <li>農耕課</li>
            <li>語文課</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>四年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>數學分數概念</li>
            <li>人與動物與農場</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>五年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>山林活動</li>
            <li>古文明 希臘</li>
            <li>植物課</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grade-section">
          <h3>六年級</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>聲光熱</li>
            <li>尺規幾何</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>副課程</h2>
        <p>內容建構中...</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>© 2026 光禾華德福實驗學校. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-small {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B4513, #228B22);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-small h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .hero-small p { font-size: 1.2rem; opacity: 0.9; }

  .section { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
  .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .content-block {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139,69,19,0.1);
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    color: #8B4513;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #FFD700;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .content-block p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .grade-section {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .grade-section h3 {
    color: #228B22;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .grade-section ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: #666;
  }

  .grade-section li {
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
  }

  .footer { background: #333; color: white; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; }
</style>
